                                                      z M11.8,9.5h-1.5V11h1.5V9.5z M10,5.8l1,1l1-1l-1-1L10,5.8z M13.8,4.5v7c0,0.8-0.7,1.5-1.5,1.5h-7c-0.8,0-1.5-0.7-1.5-1.5v-7
